Brittany approaches everything with an unbridled passion. To make it better. To solve the problem. To manage it more efficiently. summary: YBI has been recognized as the #1 ranked University Affiliated Business Incubator in the World by the University Business Incubator Index in Stockholm, Sweden.The Youngstown Business Incubator is an internationally recognized program, with a focus on the development of Software, Digital, and Additive Manufacturing/3D Printing companies in the Mahoning Valley. Our success has been well documented by Businessweek,  Inc., The Economist, Next City, Entrepreneur, Details, Governing, Wired, Salon, the German Financial Times, and the BBC, CNN, NPR, MSNBC, ABC and Tokyo Broadcasting.Our 32 portfolio companies operate out of a YBI owned five building campus in downtown Youngstown, Ohio. Our campus is also home to a federally funded research and development center, America Makes, the National Additive Manufacturing Innovation Institute (www.americamakes.us).
